<li><em>Recommended elective for all tracks.</em></li>
<li>Crossing TS Eliot’s The Waste Land, both figuratively and literally, we make an intensive study of significant works of major poets and writers who both helped to create and were created by the Modern Age, and of those they influenced.</li>
